<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="result-n">result <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'zʌlt/    美 /rɪ'zʌlt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 结果；成果：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you believe in yourself and work hard, you can <strong>achieve</strong> great <strong>results</strong>. 
相信自己并付出努力，你就会得到好结果。</p><footer> 2008 浙江</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The book is the <strong>result of</strong> 25 years of research. 
这本书是25年研究的成果。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>比赛结果；考试成绩：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the football results 
足球比赛的结果</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>get good results 
取得好成绩</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="as-a-result-of">as a result (of)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>作为 (…的) 结果：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Alice overslept this morning. As a result, she was late for work.
艾丽斯今天早上睡过了头，结果上班迟到了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>About 21 million people died during the 1990s as a result of smoking. 
20世纪90年代约有2100万人死于吸烟。</p><footer>外研② – 2</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Jenny nearly missed the flight as a result <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ doing too much shopping.  （2009 全国改）  </li>
<li>My friend Martin was very sick with a strange fever; <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (结果), he could neither eat nor sleep.  （2005 江西改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. of  2. as a result  </p></div>